# Tailwind CSS Rules

-   Use consistent spacing with Tailwind's built-in spacing scale
-   Create custom color variables in tailwind.config.ts
-   Use @layer components for repeated class combinations
-   Maintain mobile-first approach with responsive classes
-   Use container queries when appropriate
-   Avoid inline styles completely
-   Use Tailwind's built-in dark mode classes
-   Group related utility classes logically:

```tsx
className={`
  /* Layout */
  flex items-center justify-between
  /* Spacing */
  p-4 gap-2
  /* Visual */
  bg-background rounded-lg
  /* Interactive */
  hover:bg-muted
`}
```
